{"tid":869004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"G片男優機上戰空少　8分「肛肛好」片外流","createTime":"2018-10-20T03:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T04:57:44.000Z","uid":121473,"like":69,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"fea683096d5a4da427e50099552630e6caf1ff1b","tid":869004,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9wYcvGj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9wYcvGj.jpg&h=ffd2c236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dD5m8s0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdD5m8s0.jpg&h=9df6bb5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BOd731m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBOd731m.jpg&h=b4f19232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAustin Wolf。翻攝自每日郵報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同志G片男優沃爾夫(Austin Wolf)，日前搭乘達美航空的時候，跟空少到廁所啪啪啪，並將影片PO到《推特》，引起軒然大波。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報》報導，一名空少下班的時候，穿著制服搭機，被沃爾夫搭話，然後兩人跑去廁所啪啪啪，並將其中進行性行為約8分鐘的片段，上傳到《推特》跟網友分享，該段影片雖然沒過多久後就被刪除了，但還是被達美航空的同事給發現。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該名空少年紀約20多歲，完全不知道影片會被PO上網路，達美航空得知此事後震怒，已將空少停職進行調查，空少接受訪問時說：「希望能讓我一個人靜一靜，讓我的生活重回正軌。」達美航空發言人表示，「該影片並未反映我們員工在服務乘客，以及背負我們達美航空名聲，所該有的專業水準。<br />\n<br />\n沃爾夫曾參與多部同志片的演出，並以一晚1200美元(約36000新台幣)的價格，提供服務。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181020/1450790/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181020%2F1450790%2F&d=do%2BRgQdsO12VW89BEKWd9F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=99f8984b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181020%2F1450790%2F&h=a086ceae\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181020/1450790/</a>"},{"pid":"aa1e0f7283c53f1aec91412d40f991e5e9d3add0","tid":869004,"uid":49392,"like":235,"dislike":49,"score":186,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-